{"tid":277220,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【英國大選】英鎊勁跌 地獄廚神Gordon Ramsay越睇越火爆...","createTime":"2017-06-09T11:59:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-09T11:59:16.000Z","uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e01a04e98babe642173c3d2046b55543e59f7342","tid":277220,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T11:59:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170609/large/1497005304_6827.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170609%2Flarge%2F1497005304_6827.jpg&h=89503fda&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n(路透社網站圖片)<br />\n<br />\n英鎊滙價下滑，「地獄廚神」Gordon Ramsay可能越睇越眼火爆！Gordon Ramsay創辦Restaurant Gordon Ramsay，連續12年摘下米芝蓮三星，但也避不開英鎊貶值，面臨進口食材價值飆升，升幅為三年以來最勁。集團為控制成本，特設採取緊急應變措施，特設採購團隊搜羅食材，藉此降低經營成本。<br />\n<br />\n英鎊滙價自去年脫歐公投後累跌15%，英鎊兌美元今日曾低見1.2635，跌2.47%。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56806840&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170609\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56806840%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170609&d=lcEK0%2F7e%2FofNWhS4pCQShW6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=8cc72d63\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56806840%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170609&h=48d4dadc\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56806840&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170609</a>"}]}